channel.title: Starter Pack?
channel.description:
Hey guys i need some help because i have recently changed to a delta base and i have forgotten what to search for in player.java to change the starter pack is , yes i know usually its ::starter but not on delita
usually i search [code]item slot[/code] but it does not come up with anything.
any help is great thanks ,
-lewis

item.title: Starter Pack?
item.dc:creator: @lewis2 lewis`
item.description:
@lewis2 wrote:

[quote=“noobie22, post:4, topic:267413”]and under

if(command.startsWith(“starter”) && playerRights => 0

Add the items you want to put in
like this:

addItem(995, 25000000);
addItem(4151, 5);
addItem(556, 5000);
addItem(557, 1000);
addItem(558, 1000);
addItem(555, 1000);
addItem(554, 1000);
addItem(562, 1000);

That’s my starter
[/quote]

thats not for delta im afraid , delta usually there is just items in your inv when you log in
